OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain over
OL,6,Fthe east at first, clearing through
OL,7,Fthe evening and turning wintry over
OL,8,Fthe hills. Otherwise dry with
OL,9,Fincreasingly clear skies, allowing a
OL,10,Fwidespread frost to develop.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FDry with good prolonged sunny
OL,13,Fspells, though feeling cooler than
OL,14,Frecent days. Cloudier in the west with
OL,15,Fincreasingly strong south to southwest
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
