OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith some bright spells in east on
OL,7,FSaturday, windy and cloudier in west
OL,8,Fwith occasional rain. Variable cloud
OL,9,Fand bright spells Sunday and Monday
OL,10,Fwith occasional rain, mostly west.
